# Fullvue marketing copy

Read **fullvue-io-marketing-agent.md** for the full brief. This repo is the fullvue.io **marketing site**; ERP paths in that doc refer to the product codebase.

## Hard rules

- **Assets** replaces legacy **Equipment** and **IT Database (ITDB)** — one module, slug `assets`. Do not list Equipment/ITDB as separate product modules on this site.
- Match **module names** to the catalog in the brief (Sales, Field, Counter, Tether, Planner, Rentals, etc.).
- **Outcome-first** copy for owners/GMs; no unsupported superlatives or invented integrations.
- **QuickBooks Online** is the verified accounting integration; do not claim full GL replacement.
- Industry pages may mention equipment in plain English; product/module lists must use **Assets**.

## Site gaps to watch

Counter/POS, Assets, Rentals, Tether, Planner, Attendance, Customer portal — flag if missing from `/modules` or pricing.
